songs.title: Man of My City (Demo)
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus: K CAMP]
Hah, bitch, I'm the man in my city (8-8-808Mafia)
I see how they playin’, I get it
I don't say much, but she with it
Young, wild and free 'til I’m finished (Metro Boomin' want some more, nigga)

[Bridge: Travis Scott]
Got all the drugs you can handle (Yeah, yeah)
Blow all the holes through the roof (Woo)
Light up the sky like a candle
Flashin' lights out of the blue (Yeah)

[Chorus: K Camp & Travis Scott]
Hah, bitch, I'm the man in my city (Bitch, I'm the man in my city, yeah)
I see how they playin', I get it (See how they playin', I get it, I get it)
I don't say much, but she with it (I don’t see much, but I get it, hey)
Young, wild and free ’til I'm finished (Young, wild and free ’til I'm finished)

[Post-Chorus: K CAMP & Travis Scott]
Yeah (Agh)
This goin' up in my shit
Turn up, hey (Agh)

[Verse: Travis Scott]
First off, just jumped off the conference call
Second on the list, we ain't fuck with y’all
Built my own glory, I'm so awesome, y'all
Overall, I mean, you won't fuck with my overalls, but
9AM, in the club 'til 9AM
Had to-, saw the coppers, fought them poppers in the end
Bitches poppin' bottles, it's 9AM
Passin' [?], pickin' [?] 8AM
I done run up, up the block
They ain't niggas on the blocks
Same nigga [?] cookin' up the pot
Same niggas-niggas poppin' with they tops
Same niggas since a Scott, same [?] young Scott
You need a knot, pass on, nigga, get chalked
Roll one, [?] my ozone, nigga, Mojo, sold up and ain't [?]
(Yeah, alright)
